**Accessibility checks**
1. Use semantic HTML headings (`<h1>`–`<h3>`) for logical reading order.  
2. Confirm contrast with a‑checker or WAVE tools (`https://wave.webaim.org`).  
3. Include alt text in any illustrative images.  
4. Ensure the same disclaimer footer appears on the page:  
